spanGrp.span: After the war many Urum people left without houses.
dögüštän sora čoğ urum halh ğaldi ğapi_bajasız
They had no food and no clothes.
aa emäkläri yoğudi aspaplari yoğudi gäzierdılär gäzierdılär
Then some of them stayed in villages.
soram aa bazısi ee ğaldi kövlärdä
Some of them went to the city.
When they got to the villages, they realised that there was nothing there.
navahki urum halh getti ee kövlärä düštülär bahtılar ki biše yoğudi biše edämierlär
After that they decided to come to the city.
They came to Georgia and started living there.
